ArrayOpenHashIndexedLong2FloatMap, BlockOpenHashIndexedLong2FloatMap
public interface IndexedLong2FloatMap
extends IndexedMap<java.lang.Long,java.lang.Float>

A searchable indexed collection, that associates keys to values, references each such pair by a unique index, and does not allow duplicate keys..

An indexed map of objects, that associates with each unique key an entry, constituted of a unique identifier, and a modifiable value. Given a key that is mapped to an entry, the associated index can be retrieved, which can be used in reading, writing, and removal operations on the mapping value.
